page.title: 17TIMES 1985 CLAIRE WRIGHT.
page.content: BOOKS I like reading ENID BLYTON novels.I also enjoy reading comics filled with funny jokes and illustrations.There is a library in the school and there is also an excellent public library which I visit each evening after school is over. POP/MUSIC Everyone likes good music. My favourites are DURAN /DURAN,PHIL COLLINS, WHAM and many others. TRANSPORT. We have buses cars,bikes,motor/bikes,aeroplanes , helicopters and trains. My dad owns a car.On the sea we have a variety of sea/going crafts. CURRENCY We have a variety of coins and notes.I have a banking account to encourage me to save for the future. I bank with the T. S .B.
